txt.en: Wanted: Ancient sword sheaths from Azanulbizar to aid the Haban'akkâ of Thráin. Reward to be granted upon delivery.
As promised, you have received a modest reward for delivering the trophies sought by the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
Haban'akkâ of Thráin Task: Ancient Sword Sheaths
The Dwarves of the Haban'akkâ have posted a task to collect ancient sword sheaths at Azanulbizar. These can be turned in for a reward.
Deliver the ancient sword sheaths to a collection box
You have accepted a task to acquire ancient sword sheaths for the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
Wanted: Ancient sword sheaths from Azanulbizar to aid the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
